---
title: Honey-Mustard Almond Turkey with Green Bean and Cranberry Freekeh
description: Warm-up with this hearty winter freekeh bowl! Oven-roasted honey mustard turkey and sweet and tender cranberries bring robust and zesty flavours to the plate. Together, they create the perfect bite!
